net.sf.opengroove.client.plugins
Class AccumulatingSupervisor

java.lang.Object
  net.sf.opengroove.client.plugins.AccumulatingSupervisor
All Implemented Interfaces:
Supervisor
public class AccumulatingSupervisor
extends Object
implements Supervisor

A simple supervisor that can have any number of AccumulatingExtensionPoints associated with it. All extensions registered are stored in a hash map that maps extension points to the extensions registered with them.

Author:
Alexander Boyd
